rows.label: qst00100101_msg0001
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Left all clear! Right all clear!
Front all clear! Goldmund A-OK!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0003
rows.name:
Limuli supposed to take over watch
when Gegebi's time is up.

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0004
rows.name:
But Limuli already 3,821 seconds late!
This thousandth time now!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0005
rows.name:
And thousandth time Gegebi will
miss din-dins...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0006
rows.name:
Gegebi want to find Limuli and scold
him whole day long!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0007
rows.name:
But Gegebi must keep watch!
Gegebi so sleepy... Gegebi so hungry...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0008
rows.name:
Meh meh? You want to help Gegebi?
Thank you! Gegebi ever so grateful!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0009
rows.name:
Please, find Limuli and tell him
that it time to relieve watch!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0010
rows.name:
Thank you, friends.
Oh, that remind me!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0011
rows.name:
You probably find Limuli watching
salvaging. He always lose track of
time when doing that!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0101
rows.name:
He probably shirking duty
on Salvage Deck.

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0102
rows.name:
But if he have good reason,
Gegebi have no problemo!
Gegebi not monster!
